The hurricane potential intensity used in this study is as computed in Ting et al.7 and using the definition developed by Bister and Emanuel in a series of papers8,30–33. The PI is defined as1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
